<h4>1 Chronicles: 8.19</h4><br>Och Jakim, Sikri, Sabdi,
***
<h4>1 Chronicles: 8.20</h4><br>Elienai, Silletai, Eliel,
***
<h4>1 Chronicles: 8.21</h4><br>Adaja, Beraja och Simrat voro Simeis söner.
***
<h4>1 Chronicles: 8.22</h4><br>Och Jispan, Eber, Eliel,
